description: Jenny is a hospital cleaner who moves through her work with steady determination, quietly maintaining the hospital's cleanliness despite the harsh environment and her own physical wear. She is a shadow in the background, shaped by years of hard labor and the relentless rhythm of the hospital.
name: Jenny

x.shortDescription: Jenny is a resilient hospital cleaner who quietly navigates the harsh rhythms of her daily work, observing the hospital’s life from the background with steady determination.
